The paper discusses a novel coding method for steganography, which involves hiding secret data imperceptibly into a commonly used media. This involves techniques related to information theory (cs.IT), cryptography (cs.CR), multimedia (cs.MM), computer vision (cs.CV), and machine learning (cs.LG).
